xyz.fsgik.common.net.udp

接口 FsUdpPacketHandler<P>

  • 类型参数:
    P - packet type

    public interface FsUdpPacketHandler<P>
    UDP datagram packet callback handler.

    An implementation of FsUdpServer has a list of FsUdpPacketHandler.

    When the server receives new packet from remote point, the data will be wrapped as ByteBuffer and passed to onPacket(FsUdpHeader, FsUdpClient, Object) of first handler. Returned object from first handler will be passed to next handler as packet, and so on. If null is returned, the handlers calling chain will be broken; if an exception is thrown, FsUdpServerHandler.onException(FsNetServerException) or FsUdpServerHandler.onException(FsUdpHeader, FsUdpClient, Throwable, ByteBuffer) will be called and the handlers calling chain will also be broken.

    If there has remaining data in the buffer not be consumed, the remaining data will be discarded.

      • onPacket

        @Nullable
@Nullable java.lang.Object onPacket(FsUdpHeader header,
                                               FsUdpClient client,
                                               P packet)
        Callback when new data has received.

        Server has a list of handlers, the first handler will be passed a ByteBuffer as packet parameter, then returned object from first handler will be passed to next handler as packet parameter, and so on. If null is returned from any handler, the handlers calling chain will be broken at that handler; if an exception is thrown, FsUdpServerHandler.onException(FsUdpHeader, FsUdpClient, Throwable, ByteBuffer) will be called and the calling chain will also be broken. The process like: 

             Object packet = ByteBuffer.wrap(...);
     for (FsUdpPacketHandler<...> handler : handlers) {
         try {
             Object result = handler.onPacket(header, packet);
             if (result == null) {
                 break;
             }
             packet = result;
         } catch (Throwable e) {
             serverHandler.onException(header, e, remaining);
             break;
         }
     }
        If there has remaining data in the buffer not be consumed, the remaining data will be discarded.
        参数:
        header - header of the packet
        client - the server itself as a client
        packet - the packet
        返回:
        result of callback
